<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Mark Zuckerberg started Facebook beca=
use he thought having an online college facebook would be fun.</li>=09<li s=
tyle=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Zuckerberg took Facebook public while keeping =
