<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The thing about Mark Zuckerberg is that he rea=
lly did take a company public on the premise =E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m going to =
do stuff that you think is dumb, and in the long run it is going to make yo=
u so rich,=E2=80=9D and he was absolutely right. And now he is doing it all=
 over again, and maybe he is right again! Or maybe nobody is right about th=
at sort of thing more than once, and this is going to be a disaster.=C2=A0<=
/p>
