aid would consume as much as $39bn next year, more than double the level of=
 2021.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIf any other company had done this yo=
u=E2=80=99d have activist investors writing letters, proposing alternative =
slates of directors, demanding change,=E2=80=9D said Jim Tierney, chief inv=
estment officer for US growth at AllianceBernstein, a Meta shareholder. =E2=
=80=9CI think Mark heard crystal clear what investors wanted. He=E2=80=99s =
made his decision.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He heard crystal clear what investors wanted, =
and he absolutely does not care, and he set up the whole company around not=
